#: src/beeware_docs_tools/shared_content/en/_shared/contribute/how/submit-pr.md:233
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you've previously pushed the current branch to GitHub, you won't receive the URL again. However, there are other ways to get to the PR creation URL:"
