#: src/beeware_docs_tools/shared_content/en/_shared/contribute/how/write-docs.md:17
#, fuzzy
msgid "Then, you'll need to update the `docs/en/SUMMARY.md` file to include your new file. `SUMMARY.md` is organized to basically reflect the `docs/en` directory structure, but, more importantly, directly determines the structure of the left sidebar. If you locate the section where you intend to include `new_doc.md`, you do not need to change anything in `SUMMARY.md` if you see a wildcard path listed. For example:"
