#: src/beeware_docs_tools/shared_content/en/_shared/contribute/style/docs-style-guide.md:62
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can also create an anchor on general content, including text and codeblocks. The following formatting, with newlines above and below, should be included above the content to which you wish to link:"
